snippet.title: KungFu Kickball [Game Trailer]
snippet.description:
KungFu Kickball is a team based fighting sports game where the best ball-kicker wins. Punch, kick, and headbutt your way across the field to slam the ball into your opponents’ bell and rack up points!

Out now on Steam, Xbox, PlayStation and Switch! 
https://kungfukickball.com
